Name:           dbxtool
Version:        8
Release:        13%{?dist}
Summary:        Secure Boot DBX updater
License:        GPLv2
URL:            https://github.com/vathpela/dbxtool
ExclusiveArch:  i386 x86_64 aarch64
BuildRequires:  gcc
